<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Top Engineering Colleges in Andhra Pradesh</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #004080;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .college-list {
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .college {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .college:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .college-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #0056b3;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .college-info {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
        }
        footer {
            display:flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height:50px;
            background-color: #333;
            color:white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Top 10 Engineering Colleges in Andhra Pradesh</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="college-list">
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Andhra University College of Engineering, Visakhapatnam</div>
            <div class="college-info">One of the oldest and most prestigious institutions in Andhra Pradesh.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">JNTU College of Engineering, Kakinada</div>
            <div class="college-info">Known for its strong emphasis on engineering and technology programs.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">K L University, Vijayawada</div>
            <div class="college-info">Offers a range of innovative programs and has strong industry connections.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Sri Venkateswara University College of Engineering, Tirupati</div>
            <div class="college-info">Prides itself on a robust curriculum in engineering disciplines.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Gayatri Vidya Parishad College of Engineering, Visakhapatnam</div>
            <div class="college-info">Focuses on research and provides excellent technical education.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">SRKR Engineering College</div>
            <div class="college-info">Dedicated to empowering students through technical education.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Vignan's Foundation for Science, Technology & Research, Guntur</div>
            <div class="college-info">Known for its entrepreneurial atmosphere and innovative teaching.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">RVR & JC College of Engineering, Guntur</div>
            <div class="college-info">Reputed for its undergraduate and postgraduate engineering courses.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Vasireddy Venkatadri Institute of Technology, Guntur</div>
            <div class="college-info">Renowned for its advanced research facilities and high academic standards.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="college">
            <div class="college-name">Sree Vidyanikethan Engineering College, Tirupati</div>
            <div class="college-info">Excellent academic environment with a focus on holistic learning.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Made By Vijay&Sudarshan with Love &hearts;</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
